title: AI-Powered Cancer Diagnostics
description: Developed a machine learning model for early cancer detection using medical imaging data. Implemented deep learning algorithms with 95% accuracy in identifying malignant cells. The system processes CT scans and MRI images to detect early-stage tumors.

title: Quantum Computing Simulator
description: Built a quantum circuit simulator using Lean theorem prover. Implemented quantum gates and algorithms for educational purposes in quantum computing. Features include quantum entanglement visualization and algorithm testing.

title: Full-Stack E-commerce Platform
description: Developed a complete e-commerce solution with React Native frontend and Firebase backend. Features include user authentication, product management, shopping cart, payment processing with Stripe, and admin dashboard.

title: Robotics Control System
description: Designed and implemented a control system for autonomous robotics using ROS and computer vision. Integrated sensor fusion and path planning algorithms for obstacle avoidance and navigation.

title: Real-time Chat Application
description: Built a real-time chat application with WebSocket support, user authentication, and file sharing capabilities. Features include group chats, private messaging, and message encryption.

title: Data Visualization Dashboard
description: Created an interactive dashboard for visualizing complex datasets using D3.js and React. Includes multiple chart types, filtering capabilities, and real-time data updates.

title: Blockchain Smart Contracts
description: Developed smart contracts for decentralized applications using Solidity and Ethereum. Implemented token contracts, voting systems, and DeFi protocols with security best practices.

title: Computer Vision Game
description: Created a gesture-controlled game using computer vision and hand tracking. Players control game elements through hand movements and gestures captured by webcam.
